                                After your devices are received and thoroughly validated, PlanITROI provides a detailed report outlining the trade-in value of each device by receipt grade, with all serialized data, ensuring transparency and trust.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="process-step appear-animation animated fadeInUpShorter appear-animation-visible" data-appear-animation="fadeInUpShorter" data-appear-animation-delay="1000" style="animation-delay: 1000ms;">
